title: MONDAY 2/1 - Blockbuster trade
itunes:title: MONDAY 2/1 - Blockbuster trade
description:
As we get set for Super Bowl week, a blockbuster trade went down over the weekend (0:09)... Matthew Stafford traded to the Rams in exchange for Jared Goff and a host of picks. Well break it down and hear what other teams were looking at Goff. Speaking of QB's new Texans coach David Culley says Deshaun Watson is still the man in Houston (2:04). Plus Eagles head coach Nick Sirianni talks about his QB situation in Philadelphia (2:43)
